OL,3,CMan jailed for nine months and fined
OL,4,Cfor spitting in police officer's face
OL,6,FA Jersey man has been sentenced to
OL,7,Fnine months and received a fine of
OL,8,F#1,000 for spitting in a police
OL,9,Fofficer's face.
OL,11,FJay Wallace appeared at Jersey
OL,12,FMagistrate's Court on Monday (6
OL,13,FJanuary) and was handed a total of 12
OL,14,Fmonths imprisonment which included
OL,15,Fother charges.
