OL,3,CMan jailed for nine months and fined
OL,4,Cfor spitting in police officer's face
OL,6,FChief of Police, Robin Smith, said:
OL,7,F"The Court heard today that Wallace
OL,8,Fhas the most appalling criminal
OL,9,Fhistory, including previous assaults
OL,10,Fon police in Jersey and in another
OL,11,Fjurisdiction.
OL,13,F"Wallace racially abused one officer
OL,14,Fand spat in another officer's face. It
OL,15,Fhas been particularly distressing for
OL,16,Fthe officers, and I'm proud of her
OL,17,Fprofessionalism and dedication.
