OL,3,CMan jailed for nine months and fined
OL,4,Cfor spitting in police officer's face
OL,6,F"Today's sentence and the Assistant
OL,7,FMagistrate's comments in court have
OL,8,Fsent the strongest deterrent yet, that
OL,9,Fassaults on emergency service workers
OL,10,Fwill not be tolerated."
OL,12,FJersey Police say incidents of
OL,13,Fspitting offences against officers
OL,14,Fhave increased over recent years.
OL,16,FThe force recorded 18 incidents in
OL,17,F2024 - doubling from 2022 and being
OL,18,Fthe highest recorded number for the
OL,19,Fpast five years.
