OL,4,Cfor spitting in police officer's face
OL,6,FThey add that there's been an 83.3%
OL,7,Fincrease in assaults (of all kinds) on
OL,8,Fpolice officers since 2022.
OL,10,FPolice officers who are spat at while
OL,11,Fdoing their jobs, particularly in the
OL,12,Fface, have to undergo health
OL,13,Fassessments at the hospital for
OL,14,Finfectious diseases.
OL,16,FIn December 2024, police released
OL,17,Fbodycam footage in a separate incident
OL,18,Fwhere an unidentified person spat in
OL,19,Fthe face of an officer on duty.
